\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7233194 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 She married a chap who also worked at Wolsey and he was a hosiery knitter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12020912 RR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7233194 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 George was your first son was born on the 3rd March 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12020912 RR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7233194 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 And he started his working life as an engineers apprentice at Smiths of Baysford in Nottingham?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12020912 RR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7233194 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 Until he was about seventeen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12020912 RR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7233194 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 Then he had a long illness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12020912 RR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7233194 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 Then he worked at Boots in Nottingham?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12020912 RR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4936228\charrsid10957874 Yes.
